java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, weka.classifiers.Classifier, weka.core.CapabilitiesHandler, weka.core.OptionHandler, weka.core.Randomizable, weka.core.RevisionHandler
public class CCq
extends MultilabelClassifier
implements weka.core.Randomizable

The Classifier Chains Method - Random Subspace ('quick') Version. This version is able to downsample the number of training instances across the binary models. See: Jesse Read, Bernhard Pfahringer, Geoff Holmes, Eibe Frank. Classifier Chains for Multi-label Classification. Machine Learning Journal. Springer. Vol. 85(3), pp 333-359. (May 2011).

January 2009
Author:
